title: vllm-cost-meter
abstract: >-
  An objective, live effective-cost-per-million-tokens meter for self-hosted
  vLLM inference servers; companion artifact to the paper "Beyond Per-Token
  Pricing: A Concurrency-Aware Methodology for LLM Infrastructure Cost
  Estimation."
